[+] Bugs

Please use http://bts.eresi-project.org/

Compile libkernsh in debug mode, change in libkernsh/include/libkernsh.h 
the define :
	#define	__DEBUG_KERNSH__			0
in
	#define	__DEBUG_KERNSH__			1
	

